1	# Newsletter – Month {{date:MMMM}}
2	
3	#### --- Recent Blogposts ---
4	
5	```dataviewjs
6	const cutoff = dv.date("today").minus({ days: 30 });
7	
8	const blogposts = dv.pages('"Brainfood/Blogposts"')
9	    .where(p => p.date && dv.date(p.date) >= cutoff)
10	    .sort(p => dv.date(p.date), 'desc');
11	
12	for (let page of blogposts) {
13	    dv.paragraph(`- **${page.title || page.file.name}** (${dv.date(page.date).toFormat("yyyy-MM-dd")})`);
14	}
15	```
